‚çù Grid Flex Demo - Tests Grid in flex and fixed positioning modes
‚çù Three scenarios: flex row, flex column, and fixed (with Posn)

 F‚Üê'F1'
 F eWC'Form' 'Grid Flex vs Fixed'(50 50)(550 750)('Coord' 'Pixel')('Flex' 'fill')

‚çù Shared data: 3 rows x 3 columns
 values‚Üê3 3‚ç¥‚ç¨
 values[1;]‚Üê'Apple' 10 'A'
 values[2;]‚Üê'Banana' 20 'B'
 values[3;]‚Üê'Cherry' 30 'C'

 colTitles‚Üê'Name' 'Qty' 'Grade'
 rowTitles‚Üê‚ç≥3
 cellWidths‚Üê100 60 60

‚çù --- Section 1: Flex Row --- two Grids side by side (no Posn)
