 (F,'.ROW.G2')eWC'Grid'('Size'(70 253))('Values' values)('ColTitles' colTitles)('RowTitles' rowTitles)('CellWidths' cellWidths)('TitleWidth' 30)('CurCell'(1 1))

‚çù --- Section 2: Flex Column --- label then Grid vertically (no Posn)
